					</li>

					<li>
									<p>
					<em><m>\frac{1}{x} + \frac{2}{x+1} = 0</m>. Solve for <m>x</m>.</em>
				</p>
					</li>

					<li>
									<p>
					<em><m>\frac{1}{2x+7} = \frac{3}{x-1}</m>. Solve for <m>x</m>.</em>
